headline: Build-A-Bear Workshop, Inc. Names James A. Goldman to Board of Directors
summary: ST. LOUIS, February 10, 2026--Build-A-Bear Workshop, Inc. (NYSE: BBW) is pleased to announce the appointment of James A. Goldman to its Board of Directors, effective immediately.
